I was reading about Harmony, and strangly enough, it isn't clear how to use the spell. Should I cast it on me, on one monsters, on several monsters or since it is an area effect, get near several monsters and cast on me or them. Frankly, getting near several mobs doesn't sound right since I am not a malee character.<BR> Can anyone specify how this spell is to be used? Thanks.
