<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Harmony is also good to cast on ones self in certain situations.<BR>Sisters camp in LFay for example. I camped there solo from lev 9-14. Walk onto the fire in the camp and cast on yourself. Since it's AoE, you have just harmonied 3 of the 4 sisters, leaving the last one as an easy pull. You have to be careful that you pull them so that one does not come close to another, or you get an extra sister or 2 as well. This also saves you mana by only having to cast on 1 rather than 4 (all that extra mana for nuking).
</FONT>
