I cast harmony on all the MOBS except the one I want to pull.  If the MOBS are extremly close together the spell will not work.  If the MOB you pull crosses the path of harmonied MOB it will not work.  I love the spell though.  Practice it till you get it down.  It's well worth it in the long run.
